data.description: Attention VA borrowers - Ask how to get a 2.5% mortgage rate via an assumption on this home!!!! BEST of the BEST in Sugar Mill! Beautiful Custom Built Home with 4BR/3BA Plus Office, Outdoor Kitchen, on Premium Lot with ALL THE BELLS AND WHISTLES! Home has over $30,000 worth of premium upgrades including cypress beams, custom tile shower w/seamless glass, gas top stove with wall oven, extended upper cabinets with pot filler and granite kitchen sink, quartz in kitchen and baths,  the list is almost endless! Sellers also added an extended driveway, patio extension and cover, and a outdoor kitchen for enjoyment of relaxation or entertaining. Floor plan is open/split and spacious with oversized island and formal dining. Home sits on almost 1/2 acre of privacy fenced yard! Call for your private viewing! You WILL fall in love! No flood insurance required. Brusly school district! Seller will assit with closing cost!
